OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover invest #500million
OL,4,Cin car plant
OL,6,FJaguar Land Rover has said it will
OL,7,Fspend half a billion pounds to upgrade
OL,8,Fa Merseyside factory to build hybrid
OL,9,Fcars and prepare for electric vehicle
OL,10,F(EV) production.
OL,12,FBritain's largest automotive employer
OL,13,F` officially known as JLR ` said it
OL,14,Fhas already spent #250m on new car
OL,15,Fproduction lines, machinery, people
OL,16,Fand digital technology at the Halewood
OL,17,Fplant, with plans for #250m more over
OL,18,Fthe coming years.
