OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover invest #500million
OL,4,Cin car plant
OL,6,FThe investment will eventually allow
OL,7,FHalewood to produce electric versions
OL,8,Fof its medium-sized SUVs, the
OL,9,FDiscovery Sport and the Range Rover
OL,10,FEvoque, as well as traditional
OL,11,Finternal combustion engine versions
OL,12,Fand hybrids.
OL,14,FTrevor Leeks, Operations Director for
OL,15,FJLR Halewood said: "This is part of
OL,16,Four journey to full electrification
OL,17,Fwhere we're going to be carbon net
OL,18,Fzero by 2039 ` electric vehicle
OL,19,Foptions in every one of our cars by
OL,20,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
