OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover invest #500million
OL,4,Cin car plant
OL,6,F"We're going to be producing full
OL,7,Felectric vehicles at the same time as
OL,8,Four current cars with internal
OL,9,Fcombustion engines and plugin hybrid
OL,10,Felectric vehicles as well.
OL,12,F"The plant has already expanded to
OL,13,Fallow for electric vehicle production
OL,14,Fto run alongside the production of its
OL,15,Fhybrid, diesel and petrol-powered
OL,16,FRange Rover Evoque and Discovery Sport
OL,17,Fmodels."
OL,19,FJLR has said it is creating a "factory
OL,20,Fof the future" at the plant which has
OL,21,Fexisted since 1963.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
