OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover invest #500million
OL,4,Cin car plant
OL,6,FHowever, JLR, which is owned by the
OL,7,FIndian conglomerate Tata, are yet to
OL,8,Fdecide which all-electric electric
OL,9,Fmodel it will produce first.
OL,11,FMr Leeks continued: "The workforce
OL,12,Fhere are highly skilled. We've been
OL,13,Fmanufacturing and launching cars for
OL,14,Fthe last 60 years so it made sense for
OL,15,Fit to come here.
OL,17,F"The workforce here are well-versed
OL,18,Fwith being trained into new products,
OL,19,Fnew variants, new production lines and
OL,20,Fnew production systems."
